snippet.title: Shadow Warrior 3 - Full Gameplay Trailer | PS5, PS4
snippet.description:
Check out an extended look at a new mission from Shadow Warrior 3 - the Dragon’s Nest! Our hero and his chatty companion are on the hunt for the dragon that was accidentally let into our dimension at the end of the last game and, more specifically, one of its eggs that can be weaponized to defeat it. 

Shadow Warrior 3 slices its way onto PlayStation® on March 1, pre-order now!
